                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 7.5l-.625 10.632a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.247 2.118H6.622a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.247-2.118L3.75 7.5M10 11.25h4M3.375 7.5h13.125c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v4.125c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125H3.375c-.621 0-1.125-.504-1.125-1.125V8.625C2.25 8.004 2.754 7.5 3.375 7.5" /></svg>
                    Stocks
